{n : Type u_2} →
  (A : Matrix n n ℂ) →
    ∃ (P : Matrix n n ℂ) [inst : Invertible P],
      Matrix.isDiagonal (P⁻¹ ⬝ A ⬝ P)

{n : Type u_2} →

      [inst_1 : DecidableEq n] →
        [inst_2 : Field α] →
          [inst_3 : StarRing α] → (A : Matrix n n α) →
            Diagonalizable A :=
  ∃ (P : Matrix n n α), Invertible P ∧ ∃ (D : Matrix n n α), Matrix.IsDiagonal D ∧ P⁻¹ ⬝ A ⬝ P = D
